references: We further integrated CSRec with four baseline SR models: SASRec, BERT4Rec, FMLPRec and BSARec, on interventional data for GPT4-books. We show in Table 4 the improvement of incorporating CSRec into the four recommendation models in absolute scores as well as the percentage change.
